<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Advisory Commission to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s1551">section 1551 of this title</ref> and <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s1552">section 1552 of this title</ref>, $500,000 for each of fiscal years 1995 and 1996.</p>
